</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="546">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Judeo-Arabic, with a brief work in Hebrew (f. 25r-39v); notes in Samaritan (f. 1v-7v, 21r-22v, 3 bifolia laid in after f. 22v, marginal notes as on f. 281v), Arabic (f. 1r, marginal notes on Samaritan bifolia), and Latin letters (f. 20v, 25v, 238r, 239v).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
